'''''Casino: Love and Honor in Las Vegas'''''<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=nrmEQgAACAAJ&dq=isbn:0684808323&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi659ClhcHLAhXGORoKHXyKDWsQ6AEIHTAA Google Books: Casino: Love and Honor in Las Vegas]</ref> ({{ISBN|0684808323}}) is a 1995 non-fiction book by crime [[journalist|reporter]] [[Nicholas Pileggi]] that depicts the story of the alliance of [[American Mafia|Mafia]] mobsters [[Lefty Rosenthal]] and [[Tony Spilotro]] and their exploits working in Mafia controlled casinos in [[Las Vegas]].
